node.text:
Welp, this is the Raptors last weekend. Farewell bud. You did good. You will be missed and forever in our hearts. 🥲 I should probably give you a vacuum. And a wash. 

My kids and I will miss you. My wife will enjoy not moving you out of the garage again. 

May your next owner mob you as I did. I don’t think you’ll ever see the amount of coffee you and I shared ever again. Thanks for being awesome 🤙🏻❤️🔥 #fordraptor
